= AsmackService - A xmpp service for Android =

== Connections ==

=== TCP ===

Plain connection and feature negotiation:

tcp:ipv4
tcp:ipv4:port
tcp:[ipv6]
tcp:[ipv6]:port
tcp:domain
tcp:domain:port

=== Xmpp ===

XMPP connection as specified in the RFC.
The key feature is a DNS/SRV lookup for the target domain,
with tcp fallback.

xmpp:domain

== Connection Config ==

Connection string plus settings (e.g. maximum idle time before ping)

== Accounts ==

An account is a credentials pair (jid + pwd) associated with a connection
string.
